pageProduct.name: Wanderlust Plant Calcium + D3 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Vegan source of calcium and vitamin D3 derived from Marine Algae to support bone strength and health.

Wanderlust Plant Calcium + D3 is a consciously created vegan source of calcium and vitamin D3 derived from Marine Algae.
Vitamin D is an important vitamin that plays a role in supporting
healthy immune function, maintaining bone health and assisting the absorption of dietary calcium. A diet deficient in calcium can lead to osteoporosis in later life. Calcium may help prevent osteoporosis when dietary intake is inadequate. Calcium maintains bone density.

Size: 60 Capsules

Warnings

Contains sulfites.


Vitamin and mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

Ingredients

EACH CAPSULE CONTAINS:
Calcified lithothamnion species (Calcified Seaweed) 625 mg
Equiv. calcium 200 mg
Equiv. magnesium 12.5 mg
Colecalciferol 12.5 micrograms
Equiv. vitamin D3 500 IU

No added gluten, dairy, lactose, soy, egg, artificial colours or artificial flavours. Suitable for vegetarians and vegans.

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
Take two capsules daily or as directed by your healthcare practitioner.

Vitamin and mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry
place. Do not use if cap seal or
inner seal is missing or broken.
